claim.claim-text:
1. A method comprising:
fabricating a first composite capacitor residing in a first standard cell with a first set of process parameters according to a layout design data file;
using a capacitance value from said first composite capacitor to adjust a geometry of a second composite capacitor residing in a second standard cell by providing an automatic trimming adjustment to said layout design data file, wherein said second composite capacitor is fabricated with a second set of process parameters.
